<title type="html"><![CDATA[please help me debug]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=1963&amp;p=16843#p16843"><![CDATA[
Nintendulator does not support "watches" (memory I/O breakpoints), only address execution breakpoints. If you want to watch for a memory write, you'll have to use a different emulator for that.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Sat Sep 02, 2006 3:58 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
