<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=1963&amp;p=16760#p16760"><![CDATA[
You set a watch on writes to 'look'. How to find where 'look' has been placed in RAM depends on your assembler (see if it can output a "symbol table"); how to set the watch depends on your emulator.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Aug 31, 2006 7:20 pm</p><hr />
